53643.jpg\" width=\"500\" /></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:24.1pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;color:black;font-family:宋体;\">&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:24.1pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\">中餐后乘船游览国家水利风景区核心景点和国家<span>AAAA</span>级景区<span style=\"color:red;\">【<b>酒仙湖风景区】</b></span>。领略湖区湿地景观，玩尽湖区各项水上娱乐、主题岛屿及度假设施（<span>2</span>个小时），可在博物馆特产店或农贸市场选购攸县特产（攸县香干、攸县米线、攸县腐乳、网岭茶叶、酒埠江野菜等）。之后前往千年古刹<span style=\"color:red;\">【<b>宝宁寺】</b></span><span>(</span>约<span>40</span>分钟<span>)</span>，宝宁寺开创于唐天宝<span>10</span>年，为佛教南宗曹洞宗祖庭，是湖南开创最早的佛教禅院之一，佛界素有<span>“</span>北有少林，南有宝宁<span>”</span>之称，一代佛教泰斗吴立民曾用<span>“</span>足称国宝<span>”</span>评价宝宁寺。<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:24.1pt;text-align:left;\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\">下午乘车返回，结束愉快的旅程！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:24.1pt;text-align:left;\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\">&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:15pt;color:blue;font-family:宋体;\">服务标准：</span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:12pt;color:black;font-family:宋体;\"> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\">、交通：空调旅游车<span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><span>2</span>、餐饮：不含餐 </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\">、门票：上述所列景点第一门票<span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><span>4</span>、导服：优秀导游服务</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"> \r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:15pt;color:blue;font-family:宋体;\">发团时间与发团地点：<span></span></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:27.85pt;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:14pt;color:black;font-family:宋体;\">湘潭：<span>7</span>：<span>30 </span>湘潭建设路口莲城步行街<span></span></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:27.85pt;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:14pt;color:black;font-family:宋体;\">株洲：<span>8</span>：<span>10 </span>株洲河西天元超市<span></span></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:27.85pt;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:14pt;color:black;font-family:宋体;\">长沙：<span>7</span>：<span>30 </span>长沙火车站阿波罗广场<span></span></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</p>','洞天福地，魅力酒埠江','株洲方特,株洲方特欢乐世界,株洲方特欢乐世界门票,株洲方特游乐园\r\n攸县酒埠江风景区门票预订、散拼团每周六发团',''),(9,'大围山龙须峡谷漂流',8,'/upload/other/1337846784.3036713.jpg',1337788800,1337788800,502,'<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\"> </span><span style=\"color:#E53333;font-family:宋体;font-size:18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#E53333;font-size:18px;\">龙须峡谷漂</span></strong></span></b><span style=\"color:#E53333;font-family:宋体;font-size:18px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#E53333;font-size:18px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">流</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">坐落于浏阳河源头，原生态的大围山国家森林公园龙须峡谷景区内，其漂流水来源于大围山原始森林的多条峡谷，水质优良，空气清新，环境优雅。</span><span style=\"font-family: ;\" Roman?;font-size:10.5pt;?=\"\" New=\"\" Times=\"\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\"> 龙须峡谷漂流，漂流全程</span><span style=\"font-family: ;\" Roman?;font-size:10.5pt;?=\"\" New=\"\" Times=\"\">3.8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">公里，落差</span><span style=\"font-family: ;\" Roman?;font-size:10.5pt;?=\"\" New=\"\" Times=\"\">168</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">米，弯道</span><span style=\"font-family: ;\" Roman?;font-size:10.5pt;?=\"\" New=\"\" Times=\"\">29</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">个。属于强刺激的双人自助漂流。起漂点是全国首创的空中旋转漂流，惊险刺激，享有空中探险漂流美誉。河道两岸山青水秀，树木葱茏，鸟语花香，天然景点繁多，聚泉成河的溪流，连续不断的险滩区，几十个落差将冲击的心理承受极限，漂程约</span><span style=\"font-family: ;\" Roman?;font-size:10.5pt;?=\"\" New=\"\" Times=\"\">80</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">分钟。漂流后可在水上乐园享受各种水上娱乐设施，龙须峡谷漂流是年轻人猎<span style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;\"></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;\"></span>奇探险之地，更是都市白领们休闲度假的绝妙之处</span>','龙须峡谷漂流坐落于浏阳河源头，原生态的大围山国家森林公园龙须峡谷景区内，其漂流水来源于大围山原始森林的多条峡谷，水质优良，空气清新，环境优雅。\r\n ','浏阳大围山龙须峡谷漂流','');
